Play</title><meta name="description" content="WeatherPro has been created by MeteoGroup, Europes leading private weather company. This reliable, award winning app, offers unrivalled, high-quality, detailed information, including Android wearable support. These features are all brought to you by passionate weather professionals hence the name WeatherPro!

 3-hourly forecasts for the week ahead including temperature, wind direction and speed, air pressure, precipitation amount and probability and relative humidity
 View forecast as a graph for an alternative, easy to read outlook
 Worldwide alerts and warning levels for extreme weather
 Global satellite and animated radar for the USA, Australia and much of Europe
 Unlimited favourite locations plus My location to automatically show the weather where you are
 Connection to your personal weather stations, in partnership with Netatmo
 Additional features: Weather photo, Weather news, Weather reports for over 2 million locations worldwide
 Customizable widgets (choose your own colour, size, transparency, location, gradient etc.)
 Live Wallpaper with current weather images
 No adverts!

We also offer an optional premium service which is perfect for if you have specific weather interests, for sports, holidays or more:

 Hourly forecasts for 2 weeks ahead
 Windtheme: Windtheme helps users find the optimum wind conditions, by changing the entire interface of WeatherPro to show a central focus on wind data.
 Stunning, high resolution weather maps with multiple layers of advanced weather information including precipitation type radar in Europe, radar forecasts, heat maps, lightning strikes and cloud cover forecasts.
 Beach Weather with UV Index and water temperatures for the Mediterranean, Caribbean and other popular holiday destinations.
 And more

One subscription covers Premium services on all weather apps by MeteoGroup: WeatherPro, MeteoEarth and AlertsPro."><meta property="og:image" content="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/6xc-oTXSqErvWwYG7B5gw7ki7RFcCnVhoxZGAebNVb8WQ-JuqJQLbOT7aAjV3y5vZQ"><script nonce="6XpD39JNu38w5JHYzMwvvX0RF3Q">var AF_initDataKeys = ["ds:0","ds:1","ds:2","ds:3","ds:4","ds:5","ds:6","ds:7","ds:8","ds:9","ds:10","ds:11","ds:12","ds:13","ds:14","ds:15","ds:16"]

" jscontroller="wqd1Zc" data-node-index="0;0" jsmodel="hc6Ubd"><div class="JHTxhe"><div class="W4P4ne "><div class="wSaTQd"></div><meta itemprop="description" content="WeatherPro has been created by MeteoGroup, Europes leading private weather company. This reliable, award winning app, offers unrivalled, high-quality, detailed information, including Android wearable support. These features are all brought to you by passionate weather professionals hence the name WeatherPro!

 3-hourly forecasts for the week ahead including temperature, wind direction and speed, air pressure, precipitation amount and probability and relative humidity
 View forecast as a graph for an alternative, easy to read outlook
 Worldwide alerts and warning levels for extreme weather
 Global satellite and animated radar for the USA, Australia and much of Europe
 Unlimited favourite locations plus My location to automatically show the weather where you are
 Connection to your personal weather stations, in partnership with Netatmo
 Additional features: Weather photo, Weather news, Weather reports for over 2 million locations worldwide
 Customizable widgets (choose your own colour, size, transparency, location, gradient etc.)
 Live Wallpaper with current weather images
 No adverts!

We also offer an optional premium service which is perfect for if you have specific weather interests, for sports, holidays or more:

 Hourly forecasts for 2 weeks ahead
 Windtheme: Windtheme helps users find the optimum wind conditions, by changing the entire interface of WeatherPro to show a central focus on wind data.
 Stunning, high resolution weather maps with multiple layers of advanced weather information including precipitation type radar in Europe, radar forecasts, heat maps, lightning strikes and cloud cover forecasts.
 Beach Weather with UV Index and water temperatures for the Mediterranean, Caribbean and other popular holiday destinations.
 And more

One subscription covers Premium services on all weather apps by MeteoGroup: WeatherPro, MeteoEarth and AlertsPro.

,null,null,null,null,[[null,"WeatherPro has been created by MeteoGroup, Europes leading private weather company. This reliable, award winning app, offers unrivalled, high-quality, detailed information, including Android wearable support. These features are all brought to you by passionate weather professionals hence the name WeatherPro!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\t3-hourly forecasts for the week ahead including temperature, wind direction and speed, air pressure, precipitation amount and probability and relative humidity\u003cbr\u003e\tView forecast as a graph for an alternative, easy to read outlook\u003cbr\u003e\tWorldwide alerts and warning levels for extreme weather\u003cbr\u003e\tGlobal satellite and animated radar for the USA, Australia and much of Europe\u003cbr\u003e\tUnlimited favourite locations plus My location to automatically show the weather where you are\u003cbr\u003e\tConnection to your personal weather stations, in partnership with Netatmo\u003cbr\u003e\tAdditional features: Weather photo, Weather news, Weather reports for over 2 million locations worldwide\u003cbr\u003e\tCustomizable widgets (choose your own colour, size, transparency, location, gradient etc.)\u003cbr\u003e\tLive Wallpaper with current weather images\u003cbr\u003e\tNo adverts!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eWe also offer an optional premium service which is perfect for if you have specific weather interests, for sports, holidays or more:\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\tHourly forecasts for 2 weeks ahead\u003cbr\u003e\tWindtheme: Windtheme helps users find the optimum wind conditions, by changing the entire interface of WeatherPro to show a central focus on wind data.\u003cbr\u003e\tStunning, high resolution weather maps with multiple layers of advanced weather information including precipitation type radar in Europe, radar forecasts, heat maps, lightning strikes and cloud cover forecasts.\u003cbr\u003e\tBeach Weather with UV Index and water temperatures for the Mediterranean, Caribbean and other popular holiday destinations.\u003cbr\u003e\tAnd more\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eOne subscription covers Premium services on all weather apps by MeteoGroup: WeatherPro, MeteoEarth and AlertsPro."]
,[null,"Weather forecast, rain radar, weather alerts, widgets, live wallpaper. No Ads!"]
]
